 <https://www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-941> with IRS by July 31\, 2025
  to report the federal income tax\, Social Security Tax and Medicare tax y
 ou withheld from your employees' pay during the second quarter of 2025 (Ap
 ril\, May and June).\n\nTip: If your company was timely in depositing all 
 taxes when they were due\, the filing deadline is extended to Aug. 10\, 20
 25. However\, since the extended deadline falls on a weekend\, the extende
 d deadline is the next business day\, which is Aug. 11\, 2025.\n\n
