BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Who: Employers who sponsor group health plans covering retirees
  who are entitled to enroll in Medicare Part D but elect not to do so.\n\n
 What: To participate in the RDS program\, eligible employers must submit a
 n application<https://www.rds.cms.hhs.gov/> to CMS before the beginning of
  the plan year by a date specified by CMS (usually about 90 days before th
 e beginning of the plan year).\nNote: Retiree Drug Subsidy (RDS) One of se
 veral options available under Medicare that helps employers continue to as
 sist Medicare-eligible retirees in obtaining more generous drug coverage.\
 n\nTip: The approximate deadline is Oct. 2\, 2025\, for plan years beginni
 ng on Jan. 1\, 2026. This deadline may be extended by 30 days if CMS grant
 s an extension.\n\n
