 ollection is closed\, employers should monitor the EEOC website for announ
 cements regarding the 2025 cycle (expected in 2026)\, as dates\, rules (li
 ke those from Executive Order 14168<https://www.google.com/search?q=Execut
 ive+Order+14168&oq=EEO-1+Component+1+data+collection+%28monitor+EEOC+openi
 ng%2Fclosing+dates%29&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBBzIyOWowajSoAgCwAgA&
 sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8&ved=2ahUKEwj43dz6lp6SAxXkGjQIHc6gLDkQgK4QegQIARAD
 >)\, and communication methods can change annually.\n\nWhen: Deadline vari
 es by year\; monitor EEOC for 2026 filing window (often around March). (EE
 OC<https://www.eeoc.gov/data/eeo-data-collections>)\n\n\n
