 ution (DC) plans like 401(k)s are dictated by the SECURE 2.0 Act\, which g
 enerally sets the RMD starting age at 73 for those born between 1951 and 1
 959. For individuals turning 73 in 2025 (born in 1952)\, the first RMD mus
 t be taken by April 1\, 2026.\n\nWhen: Distribute first RMDs by April 1\, 
 2026\, as outlined in the plan and IRS rules.\n\n\n\n
