 n\nWhat: File federal income tax returns\n\nWhen: April 15\, 2026\, is the
  confirmed deadline for most individual federal income tax returns (Form 1
 040) and calendar-year C Corporation returns (Form 1120) for the 2025 tax 
 year\, with extensions available until October 15\, 2026\, though paying t
 axes by April is still required to avoid penalties. For S Corporations<htt
 ps://www.google.com/search?q=S+Corporations&oq=Tax+Day+%28filing+deadline+
 for+personal+tax+returns+%26+C+Corporations%29+-+04%2F15%2F2026&gs_lcrp=Eg
