 mporary annual summary that summarizes your previous year’s records\, no
 t the ongoing Log (Form 300) itself\, which stays available. The key is th
 at only the Summary (300A) gets posted\, not the detailed Log (300)\; you 
 keep the 300A for the public posting\, then file it away with other record
 s for future access by OSHA\, employees\, etc. as its a distinct requireme
 nt from the permanent Log.\n\nWhen: Remove OSHA 300A any time on or after 
 April 30\; posting period is Feb 1–Apr 30.\n
