 rance carriers are required to submit Prescription Drug Data Collection (R
 xDC) reports to the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services (CMS) annuall
 y by June 1. For the 2025 reference year\, the data—covering prescriptio
 n drug and healthcare spending—\nmust be submitted via the Health Insura
 nce Oversight System (HIOS) by June 1\, 2026\n.\n\nSubmit 2025 RxDC data (
 prescription drug and healthcare spending) to CMS<https://portal.cms.gov/p
 ortal/> by June 1\, 2026\; most employers rely on carriers/TPAs/PBMs but r
 emain ultimately responsible.\n
