BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:Who: Employers sponsoring group health plans\n\nWhat: Often pro
 vided with open enrollment/renewal: SBC\; CHIPRA annual notice\; WHCRA not
 ice\; COBRA general notice\; HIPAA special enrollment notice\; HIPAA priva
 cy notice (self-insured) and 3-year reminder\; patient protections\; grand
 fathered plan notice (if applicable)\; wellness program notices (HIPAA/ADA
 )\, etc.\n\nWhen: Open Enrollment for 2026 health insurance on the Afforda
 ble Care Act (ACA) Marketplaces generally starts on November 1\, and runs 
 through January 15\, for most states using HealthCare.gov or their own pla
 tforms\, allowing coverage to begin as early as January 1\, if enrolled by
  December 15\, or February 1\, if enrolled by the final January 15 deadlin
 e. Some states have slightly different dates\, so checking your specific s
 tate's marketplace is recommended.\n
