 m 5558 depending on the timing and applicable rules.\n\nWhat: When a Form 
 5500 due date<https://www.google.com/search?q=Form+5500+due+date&sca_esv=e
 d563ec5a8e75430&sxsrf=ANbL-n7SITot6aQ-_wjA6BS-FgCjM8YceQ%3A1769050774629&e
 i=lpJxaceVJsXz0PEP-Oa7oAM&ved=2ahUKEwjDiuyslJ6SAxUbFjQIHeu4ATAQgK4QegQIARA
 B&uact=5&oq=SAR+to+Participants+When+5500+Due+Date+is+Extended+via+Sponsor
 +Tax-Return+Extension&gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd2l6LXNlcnAiU1NBUiB0byBQYXJ0aWNpcGFudH
 MgV2hlbiA1NTAwIER1ZSBEYXRlIGlzIEV4dGVuZGVkIHZpYSBTcG9uc29yIFRheC1SZXR1cm4g
 RXh0ZW5zaW9uMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMg
 cQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCSKsHUPwFWPwFcAF4
 AZABAJgBAKABAKoBALgBA8gBAPgBAfgBApgCAaACBqgCCpgDBvEFiAMUDm4d9lKSBwExoAcAsg
 cAuAcAwgcDMi0xyAcFgAgA&sclient=gws-wiz-serp> is extended via a sponsor's t
 ax return extension\, the Summary Annual Report<https://www.google.com/sea
 rch?q=Summary+Annual+Report&sca_esv=ed563ec5a8e75430&sxsrf=ANbL-n7SITot6aQ
 -_wjA6BS-FgCjM8YceQ%3A1769050774629&ei=lpJxaceVJsXz0PEP-Oa7oAM&ved=2ahUKEw
 jDiuyslJ6SAxUbFjQIHeu4ATAQgK4QegQIARAC&uact=5&oq=SAR+to+Participants+When+
 5500+Due+Date+is+Extended+via+Sponsor+Tax-Return+Extension&gs_lp=Egxnd3Mtd
 2l6LXNlcnAiU1NBUiB0byBQYXJ0aWNpcGFudHMgV2hlbiA1NTAwIER1ZSBEYXRlIGlzIEV4dGV
 uZGVkIHZpYSBTcG9uc29yIFRheC1SZXR1cm4gRXh0ZW5zaW9uMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCM
 gcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCMgc
 QIxgnGOoCMgcQIxgnGOoCSKsHUPwFWPwFcAF4AZABAJgBAKABAKoBALgBA8gBAPgBAfgBApgCA
 aACBqgCCpgDBvEFiAMUDm4d9lKSBwExoAcAsgcAuAcAwgcDMi0xyAcFgAgA&sclient=gws-wi
 z-serp> (SAR) for participants must be distributed within two months after
  the end of that extension period\, not the original deadline\, with Decem
 ber 15th being the common extended date for calendar-year plans. This mean
 s if the 5500 deadline (typically July 31st) is extended\, the SAR follows
  the extended deadline (e.g.\, to December 15th for calendar years)\, prov
 ided the extension was properly requested\, often via IRS Form 5558<https:
 //www.irs.gov/forms-pubs/about-form-5558>.\n\nWhen: Provide SAR by Dec. 15
 \, 2026\n
